==Japanese==
===Particle===
'''って''' ([[tte]])
#he/she/I/they/we said

====Usage Note====
This is a quote marker, a colloquial form of [[と]], used with verbs that mean to say, to think, or to feel, or things like that.  This is often used alone, when the verb is understood.  In this case the verb is most commonly [[言う]], to say.

'''Example:'''
*母さんに聞いたら、「だめだ」って。 (Kaasan ni kītara, "dame da" tte.)
:When I asked my mom, she said "no."

